{"tid":364184,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港未來靠大家啦","createTime":"2017-08-18T07:32:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-18T07:57:20.000Z","uid":98022,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"71de9d36f0e72e639ab54ec562e243a7a3fb0324","tid":364184,"uid":98022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T07:32:56.000Z","msg":"知道有啲連登仔都事業有成，出人頭地，<br />\n有好大部分都大專學歷以上，未來都會擔當社會棟樑。<br />\n或者改變被改變嘅香港並唔係一朝一夕嘅事，或者宜家我地可以做嘅只有充實同裝備自己。<br />\n而大家出到黎社會，又可能會比其他人慢慢影響同化你，但記住堅守自己信念，毋忘初衷，唔好為眼前短暫的利益而拋下自己的底線。<br />\n<em>如若你愛這個家請不要任由她倒下</em><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"235c2c5f5df98d8e41e5f21d240ca352ca5abb4a","tid":364184,"uid":50533,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T07:34:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"40b1ce098e3a6561ad95070634e3cbe728055253","tid":364184,"uid":18245,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T07:45:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/18/154522_01dce73c66b41a7c5066185477d726df.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F18%2F154522_01dce73c66b41a7c5066185477d726df.jpg&h=d4fec4ff&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b73bee85d22f25e0254d4dba4066e582b13d3d5c","tid":364184,"uid":100016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T07:46:20.000Z","msg":"香港人嬌柔做作就叻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0a3c84863cbbc14e4c2057050d259614c8fa83d","tid":364184,"uid":97814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T07:47:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"07df53df861535a77b9641f64805d299ab33da84","tid":364184,"uid":98022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T07:55:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>螞蟻緣槐誇大國、蚍蜉撼樹談何易</blockquote><br />\n天垮下來擎得起，世披靡矣扶之直"},{"pid":"c143248f4eab4bb96ebcad4ae14393dede7763b1","tid":364184,"uid":98022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T07:57:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港人嬌柔做作就叻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n從自己做起，唔好因為人地係咁，就將自己條線愈拉愈低"}]}